{"tid":931934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為傳接受英國提5G網絡安全要求","createTime":"2018-12-07T11:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T12:20:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0b183f3402caa2929638200e01135beccddfc799","tid":931934,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》引述消息人士稱，華為已同意英國國家網絡安全中心(NCSC)的要求，以符合英國的5G網絡安全要求。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，在本周華為與NCSC舉行的會議中，華為接受解決其設備和軟件中存在的風險的一系列要求，並同意就此提交同意函，這將改變華為在英國業務的營運做法。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2010063/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%82%B3%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%905G%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2010063%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258F%25905G%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582&d=OG2FKvExQ3NIMvp287CNa9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0a903f99\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2010063/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%82%B3%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%905G%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82</a>"},{"pid":"408f5caa899fb11ad715c4854128ed8345d6c6f8","tid":931934,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得支那雖然簽左同意書，但我認為支那好隱悔地不支持英國ncsc嘅要求"},{"pid":"68a3a639021936a8570dbbfd07f989c0208bd08d","tid":931934,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得支那雖然簽左同意書，但我認為支那好隱悔地不同意英國ncsc嘅要求</blockquote>"},{"pid":"45118fd4849057a1bb46749c0820f8b2949687c1","tid":931934,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:59:31.000Z","msg":"中國是個大孩子，簽了合約也會照舊搞事"},{"pid":"660026cbae5cd77d9dc585d21f34afb0bfcab2b2","tid":931934,"uid":4